collectionMetadata.name: Singapore Police Force Digital Traffic Red Light Cameras
collectionMetadata.description: Digital Traffic Red Light System (DTRLS) consists of SPF wholly owned traffic enforcement cameras deployed at road junctions to deter and detect vehicles from committing the traffic offence of red-running. Implementation approach is in phases.
